flowchart LR
    A[Input: User Preferences\nGenre, Mood, Target Energy, Acoustic Preference]
    B[Load Songs CSV\nSong rows]
    C[For each song in CSV\nCompute song score]
    D{Apply scoring logic\nMood, Genre, Energy, Acoustic}
    E[Store song + score]
    F[Sort all songs by score\nHighest to lowest]
    G[Select Top K]
    H[Output: Ranked Recommendations]

    A --> C
    B --> C
    C --> D
    D --> E
    E --> C
    C --> F
    F --> G
    G --> H